Description_lang: The range of Disable is increased by $s1 yds. The duration of Crashing Momentum is increased by ${$s3/1000} sec and its snare now reduces movement speed by an additional $s2%.

description_blz.en_US:
The range of Disable is increased by 5 yds.
 
The duration of Crashing Momentum is increased by 3 sec and its snare now reduces movement speed by an additional 20%.
description_blz.es_MX:
El alcance de Incapacitar aumenta
5 m.
 
La duración de Inercia abrumadora aumenta 3 s y su efecto de frenado ahora reduce la velocidad de movimiento un 20% más.
description_blz.pt_BR:
O alcance de Desativar aumenta em 5 m.

A duração do Embalo Atropelante aumenta em 3 s, e a velocidade de movimento agora diminui em mais 20%.
description_blz.de_DE:
Die Reichweite von 'Lähmen' ist um 5 Meter erhöht.
 
Die Dauer von 'Krachendes Momentum' ist um 3 Sek. erhöht und sein Verlangsamungseffekt verringert die Bewegungsgeschwindigkeit jetzt um zusätzliche 20%.
description_blz.en_GB:
The range of Disable is increased by 5 yds.
 
The duration of Crashing Momentum is increased by 3 sec and its snare now reduces movement speed by an additional 20%.
description_blz.es_ES:
El alcance de Incapacitar aumenta 5 m.

La duración de Ímpetu batiente aumenta 3 s, y su frenado ahora reduce la velocidad de movimiento un 20% más.
description_blz.fr_FR:
La portée de Handicap est augmentée de 5 m.

La durée d’Élan écrasant est augmentée de 3 s et son effet de piège ralentit de 20 % supplémentaires.
description_blz.it_IT:
Aumenta la portata di Disattivazione di 5 m.

Aumenta la durata di Impeto Travolgente di 3 s e aumenta il suo effetto di rallentamento del 20%.
description_blz.ru_RU:
Дальность действия способности "Вывести из строя" увеличивается на 5 м.
 
"Мощное столкновение" действует на 3 сек. дольше и снижает скорость передвижения еще на 20%.
description_blz.ko_KR:
결박의 사정거리가 5미터만큼 증가합니다.

몰아치는 탄력의 지속시간이 3초만큼 증가하고, 대상의 이동 속도를 추가로 20%만큼 감소시킵니다.
description_blz.zh_TW:
傷筋斷骨的範圍提高5碼。

粉碎動能的持續時間延長3秒，且其緩速效果現在會使移動速度額外降低20%。
description_blz.zh_CN:
金刚震的射程延长5码。

迅威压迫的持续时间延长3秒，诱捕效果现在使移动速度额外降低20%。
